An sbt plugin to format your Scala source files with Scalariform.

Sample use:
  import sbt._
  import com.github.olim7t.sbtscalariform._
  
  class MySbtProject(info: ProjectInfo) extends DefaultProject(info) with ScalariformPlugin {
    override def scalariformOptions = Seq(VerboseScalariform) // See ScalariformOptions.scala and the Scalariform
                                                              // docs for the list of options
  }

Note: the plugin forks a new VM to invoke Scalariform; this is not by design but required, since sbt project definitions are compiled against Scala 2.7.7, while Scalariform uses 2.8.0.RC6.

